title: One Fish, Two Fish, Red Fish, Blue Fish/Oh, the Thinks You Can Think/Foot Book
description: From there to here, from here to there, funny things are everywhere. And most of them are right here in this captivating Dr. Seuss menagerie. Includes two other Dr. Seuss titles, Oh, the Thinks You Can Think! and The Foot Book. Closed cap. Color, 30 minutes.
author: Dr. Seuss
